MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Rokkitt' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Thin' = NID 1 'Rokkitt Thin'.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Rokkitt' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight' = NID 1 'Rokkitt ExtraLight'.

Rokkitt Light Regular (Rokkitt-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Rokkitt-Light', Everything looks good.

Pass

Rokkitt Light Regular (Rokkitt-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Rokkitt' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Rokkitt Light'.

Pass

Rokkitt Medium Regular (Rokkitt-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Rokkitt' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Rokkitt Medium'.

Mac NID 6

NID 6 is 'Rokkitt-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Rokkitt SemiBold Regular (Rokkitt-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Rokkitt-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Rokkitt SemiBold Regular (Rokkitt-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Rokkitt' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold' = NID 1 'Rokkitt SemiBold'.

Pass

Mac NID 6

NID 6 is 'Rokkitt-Bold', Everything looks good.

Rokkitt ExtraBold Regular (Rokkitt-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Rokkitt' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold' = NID 1 'Rokkitt ExtraBold'.

Pass

Rokkitt Black Regular (Rokkitt-Black.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Rokkitt' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Black' = NID 1 'Rokkitt Black'.

OS/2 and head

sTypeAsc/Desc and unitsPerEm

The result of sTypoAscender – sTypoDescender should match or exceed the unitsPerEm value.

The result of sTypoAscender – sTypoDescender (1137) match or exceed the unitsPerEm value (1000).
